// This file contains example HTTP requests for testing the API endpoints.

### 1. GET all games for a specific user
GET http://localhost:3001/api/users/1/games
Cookie: connect.sid=YOUR_SESSION_COOKIE

###

### 2. GET cards (no params)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/cards
Cookie: connect.sid=YOUR_SESSION_COOKIE

###

### 3. GET cards with params
GET http://localhost:3001/api/cards?bannedCards=1,2,3&num=2&visibility=false
Cookie: connect.sid=YOUR_SESSION_COOKIE

###

### 4. GET card by id
GET http://localhost:3001/api/cards/1
Cookie: connect.sid=YOUR_SESSION_COOKIE

###

### 5. POST create a new game
POST http://localhost:3001/api/games
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: connect.sid=YOUR_SESSION_COOKIE

{
  "userId": 1,
  "date": "2025-06-12 15:00:00",
  "initialCards": [1,2,3],
  "totalWon": 0
}

###

### 6. PUT update game rounds
PUT http://localhost:3001/api/games/1
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: connect.sid=YOUR_SESSION_COOKIE

{
  "roundIds": [10,11,12,13,14]
}

###

### 7. POST create rounds for a game
POST http://localhost:3001/api/games/1/rounds
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: connect.sid=YOUR_SESSION_COOKIE

{
  "rounds": [
    { "startedAt": "15:01:00", "cardId": 4, "roundNumber": 1, "won": true },
    { "startedAt": "15:05:00", "cardId": 5, "roundNumber": 2, "won": false },
    { "startedAt": "15:10:00", "cardId": 6, "roundNumber": 3, "won": true }
  ]
}

###

### 8. POST login (session)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "youruser",
  "password": "yourpassword"
}

###

### 9. GET current session
GET http://localhost:3001/api/sessions/current
Cookie: connect.sid=YOUR_SESSION_COOKIE

###

### 10. DELETE current session (logout)
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/sessions/current
Cookie: connect.sid=YOUR_SESSION_COOKIE

###